</div></div> <div class="h-[16px]"></div> <div class="flex flex-col space-y-[12px] md:space-y-[16px]"><div class="flex space-x-[16px]"><div class="grid place-content-center min-w-[24px] h-[24px] bg-whitesmoke rounded-full"><img alt="arrow" data-src="https://a.storyblok.com/f/145847/x/ec5ad646ef/arrow-up-right-1.svg" class="lazy lazy-svg-image lg:hidden text-[0px]"> <img alt="checkmark" data-src="https://a.storyblok.com/f/145847/x/09133d5206/icon.svg" class="lazy lazy-svg-image hidden lg:block text-[0px]"></div> <div class="prose prose-p:text-[14px] md:prose-p:text-[16px] md:prose-p:leading-[24px] prose-a:text-blue prose-a:no-underline tracking-[0.1px] md:tracking-[0.15px]"><p><strong>Absence Category Selection</strong></p>
